name: Hotel Swetha
description:
Finding an ideal budget friendly hotel in Karimnagar does not have to be difficult. Welcome to Hotel Swetha, a nice option for travelers like you.
The rooms offer a minibar and air conditioning, and getting online is possible, as free internet access is available, allowing you to rest and refresh with ease.
Hotel Swetha features a concierge and room service. In addition, as a valued Hotel Swetha guest, you can enjoy a fitness center and free breakfast that are available on-site. Guests arriving by vehicle have access to free parking.
Plus, during your trip, don't forget to check out a castle, such as Elgandal Fort.
Hotel Swetha puts the best of Karimnagar at your fingertips, making your stay both relaxing and enjoyable.
